  </div>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <br/>
        <h2 class="heading">Homepage - The Amazing & Marvelous Creamery!</h2>
        <br/>
        <h5 class="heading">If you're a guest, feel free to browse our list of <a href=<%=  %>> Active Stores</a>.<br/><br/></h5>
        <h6 class="heading">
            
        How good is our ice cream? Well, let's just say that on a scale of 1 to 10, we're somewhere around a 17.1423512. 
        But we’re about more than just serving up amazing ice cream. 
        We’re really in the business of making people happy...
        It's all about what we call the 15-Minute Break... that 15-minute getaway you deserve from the world outside 
        our doors. Just head inside any A&M Creamery, and that's what you'll get. From our enthusiastic, lively 
        crew members, to the shared laughter of a family enjoying  a treat together — if it’s making you, your friends, 
        or your loved ones happy, then we’re doing our jobs right!
        To learn more about us, or for more information on what we do, how we do it, or why we love it — 
        check out our <a href= <%= contact_index_path %>>Contact Us</a> page or follow the other links in the footer below!
        </h6>
        <h5 class="heading">
        
        For employees:<br/>
        On this website, you'll be able to
        manage your employee functions. Login with a smile!
        </h5><br/>
        
        <div class="center-align">
        <a class="waves-effect waves-red deep-orange darken-4 hoverable btn-large white-text" href=<%= new_demo_path  %>>Login</a></li>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>


